Thank you for making an appointment!

Your appointment is scheduled for <%= appointment_date_and_time(@appointment) %>

<% if @appointment.holds.present? %>
The following holds are associated with your appointment:
  <% @appointment.holds.each do |hold| %>
    Name: <%= hold.item.name %>
    Number: <%= hold.item.complete_number %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @appointment.loans %>
These are the loans associated with your appointment:
  <% @appointment.loans.each do |loan| %>
    Name: <%= loan.item.name %>
    Number: <%= loan.item.complete_number %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

You can make changes to this appointment here: <%= account_appointment_url(@appointment) %>